e/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-to-run-for-mayor-next-year-marty-walsh-says/33943475 |website=WCVB |accessdate=8 September 2020 |language=en |date=7 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709183859/https://www.wcvb.com/article/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-to-run-for-mayor-next-year-marty-walsh-says/33943475 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Milton"/>。她亦曾經呼籲廢除波士頓的城市規劃局<ref name="Milton"/>。同年3月，她被支持民主黨女性黨員的政治行动委员会{{Link-en|EMILY's List|EMILY's List}}選為「未來之星」<ref>{{cite news |first=James |last=Pindell |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/news/politics/2018/03/01/michelle-finalist-for-award-from-abortion-rights-group-emily-list/KWeYWrOcqhuYLcPLqNit8J/story.html |title=Michelle Wu a finalist for award from abortion rights group EMILY's List |work=The Boston Globe |date=2018-03-01 |accessdate=2018-06-22 |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711153326/https://www.bostonglobe.com/news/politics/2018/03/01/michelle-finalist-for-award-from-abortion-rights-group-emily-list/KWeYWrOcqhuYLcPLqNit8J/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後她被月刊《{{Link-en|Boston|Boston (magazine)}}》選入「100名最具影響力的波士頓人」<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/2018/04/24/most-influential-people-boston/|title=The 100 Most Influential People in Boston|work=[[Boston_(magazine)|Boston]]|date=2018-04-24|accessdate=2018-06-22|editor=David S. Bernstein|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622220331/https://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/2018/04/24/most-influential-people-boston/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2020年，吳弭公佈了在波士頓推廣[[绿色新政|绿色新政]]的計劃。她希望通過此計劃，為波士頓市民提供更低廉及可持續利用的房屋<ref>{{cite web |last1=Alston |first1=Paris |last2=Dearing |first2=Tiziana |title=Michelle Wu On Vaccine Distribution, Affordable Housing, And Boston's Mayoral Race |url=https://www.wbur.org/radioboston/2021/01/28/michelle-wu-boston |website=www.wbur.org |publisher=WBUR-FM |access-date=11 February 2021 |language=en |date=28 January 2021 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709185608/https://www.wbur.org/radioboston/2021/01/28/michelle-wu-boston |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後在2021年，她在市議會提出了有關新冠肺炎疫苗的法案，建議在每個居民區設立至少一個疫苗注射點以確保所有居民均可獲得均等的接種機會<ref>{{cite web |last1=Basile |first1=Abigail |title=Boston City Councilor Michelle Wu on her proposed equitable COVID-19 vaccine distribution |url=http://www.umassmedia.com/news/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-on-her-proposed-equitable-covid-19-vaccine-distribution/article_e4f2c632-67c1-11eb-82f8-cbd2fcfe7ba2.html |website=The Mass Media |access-date=11 February 2021 |language=en |date=8 February 2021 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712120648/http://www.umassmedia.com/news/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-on-her-proposed-equitable-covid-19-vaccine-distribution/article_e4f2c632-67c1-11eb-82f8-cbd2fcfe7ba2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

====對波士頓交通問題的態度====
{{Main|马萨诸塞湾交通局#批评}}
在2019年夏天，因爲不滿[[马萨诸塞湾交通局|马萨诸塞湾交通局]]提高[[輕軌運輸系統|轻轨]]、[[公共汽车|公共汽车]]及隧道等公共交通服務的收費，吳弭帶領了抗議活動<ref name="Milton" /> 。她認爲波士頓應該提供免費的公共交通服務。其後此項政策也成爲了她最具知名度的政策之一。
{{cquote|我們必須去除那些存在于公共交通服務中不必要的收費門檻，因爲地理上的流動性對[[社会流动|社会流动]]有著決定性的影響。公共交通服務的便利性不僅是統計街上有多少台汽車；而根據以往經驗，那些提供免費公共交通服務的城市能受惠于交通平等，包括提供了更多機會予低收入、老人與年輕的居民。在那些地域收入不平等與種族分隔的城市，不穩定的公共交通服務及高昂的收費無疑會成爲了年輕人與有色人種的額外負擔。去除這些門檻，對增加我們的勞動力有著莫大的裨益<ref name="Milton">{{cite news |last=Valencia |first=Milton J. |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2019/06/30/michelle-says-boston-ready-for-change-but-boston-ready-for-michelle/6ayPte0oomtlOXq2TBzpZN/story.html |title=Michelle Wu says Boston is ready for change. But is Boston ready for Michelle Wu? |work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]] |date=2019-07-01 |accessdate=2019-07-01 }}</ref>。|節錄于《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》的[[社论对页版|社论]]，2019年1月31日。}}

===參選波士頓市長（2020年-2021年）===
[[File:Michelle_Wu_campaigning_for_Mayor_(1)_02.jpg|thumb]]
2019年起，一些波士頓當地的媒體開始揣測吳弭將參加下一届波士頓市長選舉，以挑戰時任市長马蒂·沃尔什<ref>{{Cite web |last=Bernstein |first=David S. |date=April 10, 2019 |title=2019 Boston City Council Race Sets Stage For 2021 Mayor's Contest |url=https://www.wgbh.org/news/commentary/2019/04/10/2019-boston-city-council-race-sets-stage-for-2021-mayors-contest |access-date=April 13, 2020 |publisher=WGBH-TV |language=en |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711184408/https://www.wgbh.org/news/commentary/2019/04/10/2019-boston-city-council-race-sets-stage-for-2021-mayors-contest |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=September 4, 2020 |title=Michelle Wu ramping up campaign spending, suggesting Boston mayoral run |url=https://www.bostonherald.com/2020/09/04/michelle-wu-ramping-up-campaign-spending-suggesting-boston-mayoral-run |access-date=September 5, 2020 |website=Boston Herald |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711160526/https://www.bostonherald.com/2020/09/04/michelle-wu-ramping-up-campaign-spending-suggesting-boston-mayoral-run/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年9月7日，《波士顿环球报》報道吳弭已經向沃尔什表達參選意願<ref name=walshsays>{{cite web |last1=McDonald |first1=Danny |last2=Valencia |first2=Milton J. |title=Boston City Councilor Michelle Wu is running for mayor, Walsh says - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/09/07/metro/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-is-running-mayor-walsh-says/ |website=BostonGlobe.com |publisher=Boston Globe |accessdate=7 September 2020 |date=7 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210725082012/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/09/07/metro/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-is-running-mayor-walsh-says/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後于9月15日，吳弭在其推特帳戶上發佈影片，正式宣佈參選2021年波士頓市長選舉<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/09/15/metro/michelle-wu-makes-it-official-shes-running-mayor-boston/ |title=Michelle Wu makes it official: She's running for mayor of Boston |first=Milton J. |last=Valencia |website=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]] |date=September 15, 2020 |accessdate=September 15, 2020 |archive-date=2021-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505180930/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/09/15/metro/michelle-wu-makes-it-official-shes-running-mayor-boston/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

吳弭在參選時表示，她采取的競選策略是「以群衆的力量為波士頓帶來新的領導」<ref>{{cite web |title=Boston City Councilor Michelle Wu announces candidacy for mayor |url=https://www.wcvb.com/article/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-announces-candidacy-for-mayor/34023547# |website=WCVB |accessdate=16 September 2020 |language=en |date=15 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930010910/https://www.wcvb.com/article/boston-city-councilor-michelle-wu-announces-candidacy-for-mayor/34023547 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的競選平臺由社區主導，並主要關注公共教育、社區規劃、房屋、交通與社區醫療等議題<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bedford |first1=Tori |title=Michelle Wu Declares Her Candidacy For Mayor Of Boston, Challenging Walsh |url=https://www.wgbh.org/news/politics/2020/09/15/michelle-wu-declares-her-candidacy-for-mayor-challenging-walsh |website=wgbh.org |publisher=WGBH-FM |accessdate=16 September 2020 |language=en |date=15 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820002037/https://www.wgbh.org/news/politics/2020/09/15/michelle-wu-declares-her-candidacy-for-mayor-challenging-walsh |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她承諾如果當選的話，將考慮由市政府建立及提供高質的寬帶網絡<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bray |first1=Hiawatha |title=Mayoral candidate Wu eyes city-owned broadband network - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/02/01/business/mayoral-candidate-wu-eyes-city-owned-broadband-network/ |website=BostonGlobe.com |publisher=Boston Gloe |access-date=11 February 2021 |date=1 February 2021 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709185945/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/02/01/business/mayoral-candidate-wu-eyes-city-owned-broadband-network/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她也表示將建議市政府牽頭建立公營的學前幼兒園，為所有5歲以下的兒童提供均等的學前教育機會<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ebbert |first1=Stephanie |title=Mayoral candidate Michelle Wu calls for universal preschool, city office coordinating early education - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/03/02/metro/mayoral-candidate-wu-calls-universal-preschool-city-office-coordinating-early-education/ |website=BostonGlobe.com |publisher=Boston Glove |access-date=3 March 2021 |date=2 March 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817034814/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/03/02/metro/mayoral-candidate-wu-calls-universal-preschool-city-office-coordinating-early-education/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在環境問題上，她提倡波士頓版的[[綠色新政|綠色新政]]，並設立了在2024年前所有市政機關達到[[碳中和|碳中和]]；2030年達到100%使用[[再生能源|再生能源]]；2040年在波士頓市域内達到碳中和等一系列環境政策目標<ref name="Milton"/><ref name="GND">{{cite web |title=PLANNING FOR A BOSTON GREEN NEW DEAL  & JUST RECOVERY |url=https://assets.ctfassets.net/1hf11j69ure4/B6NLxlOVxTVMNbHEvFaQE/700f4762bae92990f91327a7e01e2f09/Boston-Green-New-Deal-August-2020-FINAL.pdf |website=assets.ctfassets.ne |publisher=Office of Boston City Councilor Michelle Wu |access-date=5 September 2021 |date=August 2020 |archive-date=2021-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210826100110/https://assets.ctfassets.net/1hf11j69ure4/B6NLxlOVxTVMNbHEvFaQE/700f4762bae92990f91327a7e01e2f09/Boston-Green-New-Deal-August-2020-FINAL.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="greennewdealwhattoknow">{{cite web |last1=Gavin |first1=Christopher |title=What to know about Michelle Wu's 'Green New Deal & Just Recovery' for Boston |url=https://www.boston.com/news/policy/2020/08/24/michelle-wu-green-new-deal-boston/ |website=www.boston.com |access-date=15 September 2021 |date=August 24, 2020 |archive-date=2021-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210915004005/https://www.boston.com/news/policy/2020/08/24/michelle-wu-green-new-deal-boston/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

