isher=Politco|access-date=10 June 2021|language=en|date=10 June 2021|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706173556/https://www.politico.com/newsletters/massachusetts-playbook/2021/06/10/massgop-fissures-on-display-millionaires-tax-heads-to-ballot-union-hits-baker-over-holyoke-493200|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直至2021年6月，在多項[[民意調查|民意調查]]中皆顯示吳弭的支持率在所有候選人中領先<ref>{{cite web |author1=Stephanie Ebbert |title=Boston mayoral poll shows Michelle Wu and Kim Janey pulling ahead - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/06/29/metro/boston-mayoral-poll-shows-michelle-wu-kim-janey-pulling-ahead/ |website=BostonGlobe.com |accessdate=2021-07-08 |date=2021-06-29 |archive-date=2021-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818023711/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/06/29/metro/boston-mayoral-poll-shows-michelle-wu-kim-janey-pulling-ahead/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Callum Borchers |title=WBUR Poll: Wu And Janey Lead Boston Mayoral Race, But Almost Half Of Voters Are Undecided |url=https://www.wbur.org/news/2021/04/14/wbur-poll-boston-mayor-candidates-issues |accessdate=2021-07-08 |work=www.wbur.org |date=2021-04-21 |language=en |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816133646/https://www.wbur.org/news/2021/04/14/wbur-poll-boston-mayor-candidates-issues |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最後她在11月2日舉行的的第二轮选举中，以得票率64.0%成功当选为第55任波士顿市长。 

===波士頓市長（2021年-）===
吳弭于2021年11月16日正式履新，宣誓就任為第55任波士頓市長<ref>{{cite news |last1=Yin |first1=Ozzy |last2=Chiang |first2=Yi-ching |title=Taiwanese-American Michelle Wu sworn in as mayor of Boston |url=https://focustaiwan.tw/politics/202111170016 |access-date=2021-11-17 |agency=Central News Agency |date=2021-11-17 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128070552/https://focustaiwan.tw/politics/202111170016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
同月22日，作爲波士頓版綠色新政計劃的一部分，她簽署了一道法令，在市政府投資項目中削減對[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]、[[烟草|烟草]]及[[監獄|監獄]]設施有關企業的投資，總值6500萬美元<ref>{{cite news |last=Murphy |first=Matt |title=Mayor Wu Signs Ordinance Divesting Boston From Fossil Fuel Profits |url=https://www.nbcboston.com/news/local/mayor-wu-signs-ordinance-divesting-boston-from-fossil-fuels/2572931/ |access-date=2021-11-23 |agency=NBC Boston |date=2021-11-22 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121043523/https://www.nbcboston.com/news/local/mayor-wu-signs-ordinance-divesting-boston-from-fossil-fuels/2572931/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年12月，爲了加强防控波士頓市内的COVID-19疫情，吳弭針對市内的食肆、健身室與公務員宣佈了新的强制疫苗措施，由2022年1月15日起12歲以上的波士頓市民必須在進入室内場所時出示至少完成接種一針疫苗的證明；而到2月15日則必須出示完整的接種證明。此項政策遭到部分市民反對，而吳弭也在波士頓電臺的一個節目中表示，自從她頒佈此項政策后就不斷的受到來自[[反疫苗|反疫苗]]人士的[[種族歧視|種族歧視]]攻擊，部分示威人士甚至幾乎整天都在她家門口前抗議，嚴重影響了她與鄰居的日常生活<ref>{{cite news |last=Kuznitz |first=Alison |title=Boston indoor vaccine mandate takes effect next month, Mayor Michelle Wu announces |url=https://www.masslive.com/politics/2021/12/boston-indoor-vaccine-mandate-takes-effect-next-month-mayor-michelle-wu-announces.html |access-date=2021-12-24 |agency=Mass Live |date=2021-12-20 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110222030/https://www.masslive.com/politics/2021/12/boston-indoor-vaccine-mandate-takes-effect-next-month-mayor-michelle-wu-announces.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Kashinsky|first=Lisa|title=Boston mayor lines up vaccine mandates amid pushback from city workers|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/12/21/boston-mayor-vaccine-mandates-525858|access-date=2021-12-24|agency=Politico|date=2021-12-21|archive-date=2022-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119101800/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/12/21/boston-mayor-vaccine-mandates-525858|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ford|first=Rosemary|title=Mayor Michelle Wu says she's received racist messages in response to vaccine requirement|url=https://www.boston.com/news/coronavirus/2021/12/23/michelle-wu-hateful-messages-vaccine-requirement/|access-date=2021-12-24|agency=Boston.com|date=2021-12-23|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301133800/https://www.boston.com/news/coronavirus/2021/12/23/michelle-wu-hateful-messages-vaccine-requirement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後由於疫情改善，她于2月18日宣佈解除强制疫苗措施<ref>{{cite news |last1=Gardizy |first1=Anissa |last2=McDonald |first2=Danny |title=Mayor Wu lifts proof of vaccine mandate due to improving COVID-19 conditions - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2022/02/18/metro/mayor-wu-lifts-boston-proof-vaccine-mandate-effective-immediately/ |accessdate=2022-02-23 |work=BostonGlobe.com |date=2022-02-18 |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318093149/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2022/02/18/metro/mayor-wu-lifts-boston-proof-vaccine-mandate-effective-immediately/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2022年2月，吳弭宣佈將按照競選時承諾，從3月1日起取消马萨诸塞湾交通局轄下3條巴士路綫的收費，爲期兩年<ref>{{cite web |title=Mayor Wu Announces Launch of Two-Year, Fare-Free Program for MBTA Bus Routes 23, 28 and 29 on March 1, 2022 |url=https://www.boston.gov/news/mayor-wu-announces-launch-two-year-fare-free-program-mbta-bus-routes-23-28-and-29-march-1-2022 |website=Boston.gov |accessdate=2022-02-23 |language=en |date=2022-02-09 |archive-date=2022-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301140122/https://www.boston.gov/news/mayor-wu-announces-launch-two-year-fare-free-program-mbta-bus-routes-23-28-and-29-march-1-2022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後她于4月宣佈了任内首份財政預算案，建議在接下來的財政年度撥款約40億美元以改善住房、社區心理健康、氣候變化、公共教育、社區規劃及交通等議題<ref>{{cite web |title=Mayor Wu Unveils First City Budget and $350 Million Federal Spending Plan, to Deliver on the Details of Core City Services and Lay the Foundation for Boston's Green New Deal |url=https://www.boston.gov/news/mayor-wu-unveils-first-city-budget-and-350-million-federal-spending-plan-deliver-details-core |website=Boston.gov |accessdate=2022-04-15 |language=en |date=2022-04-13 |archive-date=2022-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413223016/https://www.boston.gov/news/mayor-wu-unveils-first-city-budget-and-350-million-federal-spending-plan-deliver-details-core }}</ref>。

==選舉結果==
吳弭在2013年11月首次當選為波士頓市議會議員。她在所有候選人中得票排行第二，僅次于時任議員{{Link-en|Ayanna Pressley|Ayanna Pressley}}<ref>{{cite web |title=CITY OF BOSTONMUNICIPAL ELECTION - NOVEMBER 5, 2013 CITY COUNCILLOR AT LARGE |url=https://www.cityofboston.gov/images_documents/2013%20-%2011-05-13%20-%20City%20Councillor%20at%20Large%20Ward%20&%20Precinct%20Results_tcm3-41961.pdf |website=cityofboston.gov |accessdate=February 16, 2018 |archive-date=2021-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210721203318/https://www.cityofboston.gov/images_documents/2013%20-%2011-05-13%20-%20City%20Councillor%20at%20Large%20Ward%20%26%20Precinct%20Results_tcm3-41961.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後于2015年11月她再度當選<ref name=2105results>{{cite web |title=CITY OF BOSTON MUNICIPAL ELECTION - NOVEMBER 3, 2015 CITY COUNCILLOR AT LARGE |url=https://www.cityofboston.gov/images_documents/Nov%203%202015%20City%20Councillor%20at%20Large%20Ward%20%20Precinct%20Results_tcm3-52572.pdf |website=cityofboston.gov |accessdate=February 16, 2018 |archive-date=2021-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210721203125/https://www.cityofboston.gov/images_documents/Nov%203%202015%20City%20Councillor%20at%20Large%20Ward%20%20Precinct%20Results_tcm3-52572.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年11月，她第三度當選並獲得65,040票，為波士頓市議會史上第二高得票<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.boston.gov/sites/default/files/2017_-_11-07-17_-_city_councillor_at_large_ward_precinct_results.pdf |title=CITY OF BOSTON MUNICIPAL ELECTION - NOVEMBER 7, 2017 CITY COUNCILLOR AT LARGE |website=cityofboston.gov |accessdate=February 16, 2018 |archive-date=2018-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109211600/https://www.boston.gov/sites/default/files/2017_-_11-07-17_-_city_councillor_at_large_ward_precinct_results.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2019年11月她第四度當選連任並再度在所有候選人中取得最多得票<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.boston.gov/departments/elections/unofficial-election-results |title=BOSTON MUNICIPAL ELECTION NOVEMBER 2019 |website=boston.gov |accessdate=November 5, 2019 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410173141/https://www.boston.gov/departments/elections/unofficial-election-results |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年9月，她宣佈參加[[2021年波士頓市長選舉|2021年波士頓市長選舉]]，並於2021年9月14日舉行的初選排行第一<ref name="Preliminary">{{cite web |title=Unofficial election results |url=https://www.boston.gov/departments/elections/unofficial-election-results |website=Boston.gov |accessdate=2021-09-16 |language=en |date=2016-10-03 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410173141/https://www.boston.gov/departments/elections/unofficial-election-results |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成功進入于11月舉行的第二輪選舉<ref>{{cite news |title=Live blog: Updates on the Boston mayoral race preliminary election |url=https://www.boston.com/news/politics/2021/09/14/preliminary-election-day-live-blog-updates-boston-mayoral-race/?p1=hp_primary |accessdate=2021-09-15 |work=www.boston.com |archive-date=2021-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211120001537/https://www.boston.com/news/politics/2021/09/14/preliminary-election-day-live-blog-updates-boston-mayoral-race/?p1=hp_primary |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在同年11月3日舉行的第二輪選舉中，她以得票率64.0%成功當選為第56任波士頓市長。

==個人生活==
作爲長女的吳弭從哈佛大學畢業后不久，便因爲要照顧患有[[思覺失調症|思覺失調症]]的母親和兩個妹妹一度搬回芝加哥居住，其後在2009年回到波士頓<ref name=jonas>{{cite web |last1=Jonas |first1=Michael |title=Michelle Wu's personal path to politics |url=https://commonwealthmagazine.org/politics/michelle-wus-personal-path-to-politics/ |website=CommonWealth Magazine |access-date=10 January 2021 |date=28 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711171356/https://commonwealthmagazine.org/politics/michelle-wus-personal-path-to-politics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她與長年交往的男朋友Conor Pewarski于2011年12月訂婚，并於2012年9月結婚<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/30/fashion/weddings/on-bended-knee-not-always-a-look-back-on-some-memorable-proposals.html|title=On Bended Knee? Not Always: A Look Back on Some Memorable Proposals|last=Mallozzi|first=Vincent M.|date=2012-12-28|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-07-14|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711132844/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/30/fashion/weddings/on-bended-knee-not-always-a-look-back-on-some-memorable-proposals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現時，她與兩名孩子Blaise和Cass，以及其母親一同居住在波士頓的{{Link-en|罗森黛尔|Roslindale}}地區<ref name="Milton" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://michelleforboston.com/introducing-baby-blaise/|title=Introducing baby Blaise {{!}} Michelle Wu|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714183645/http://michelleforboston.com/introducing-baby-blaise/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dorchester.comunicas.org/2017/07/18/michelle-wu-shares-details-of-her-new-baby/|title=Michelle Wu shares details of her new baby|last=daniel|date=2017-07-18|website=Dorchester Post|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711114036/https://dorchester.comunicas.org/2017/07/18/michelle-wu-shares-details-of-her-new-baby/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2019/04/michelle-wu-changing-traditional-boston/587473/|title=The Next Mayor of Boston?|last=Allen|first=Rachael|date=2019-04-22|website=The Atlantic|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-date=2021-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820115558/https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2019/04/michelle-wu-changing-traditional-boston/587473/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
